==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perpend
<hw>Per*pend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>perpendere</ets>, <ets>perpensum</ets>; <ets>per</ets> +
<ets>pendere</ets> to weight.]</ety> <def>To weight carefully in the
mind.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Perpend</xex> my words.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

