==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Perpend
<hw>Per*pend"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To attend; to be
attentive.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

